column5: Where can I find crawlers and/or leeches on the way to Eagle Lake (www.stanleys.com) from Ft Frances. I dont care to bring them across.
You can get what you need at Bobby's in Vermilion Bay.
Rainy Lake Sports is located on the east side of Fort Frances on the main road leaving town.http://rainylakesports.com/
FYI - we paid $40/lb for leeches at Boobbies a week ago. Clark's Camp, on the Indian Chain) had them for the same price.
